  <Summary>Web of Deceit: Cap and Rick are zapped by a Matter Translation Beam and become characters in an evil virtual reality game created by Hydra.

If This Be P.R.O.D.O.K.: Cap and Bucky fight P.R.O.D.O.K. They win!

The Legend Reborn!: In this retelling of Cap's origin, he is revived by SHIELD in 2009 and Rick Jones must help him to not only conquer Hydra, but also learn to fit in with modern times.

Spy for the Cameras!: While keeping an eye on a German spy, Cap must not only defy Hollywood, but also a young female reporter.

